## ğŸ­ Micro-Interactions & Animations

### Button Interactions
- **Hover**: Smooth 0.2s ease-out transition
- **Click**: 0.1s scale animation (0.98x)
- **Success**: Brief green checkmark animation

### Page Transitions
- **Fade In**: 0.3s opacity transition
- **Slide Up**: Cards animate in from bottom
- **Stagger**: Sequential animation for lists

### Loading States
- **Skeleton Loading**: Shimmer effect for content
- **Progress Indicators**: Smooth color transitions
- **Pulsing Dots**: For real-time AI processing

### Form Interactions
- **Focus**: Smooth border color change
- **Validation**: Gentle shake for errors
- **Success**: Green checkmark slide-in

